import React from 'react'
import { Link } from 'react-router-dom';
import { Button, Image } from 'semantic-ui-react'

const Page_404 = () => (
    <>
  <Image centered alt="404 Page Not Found" title="Page Not Found" src={process.env.PUBLIC_URL + "/404.jpg"}  />
  <Link to="/">
      <Divider centered>
  <Button  negative >Go Home</Button>
  </Divider>
  </Link>
  </>
  
)

export default Page_404;
